ygData.subject: Re: Hunting at 14..
ygData.msgSnippet: Nope, I m a level 10 Necro and I was soloing drakes at 9. Even yellow ones. I m guessing that they are level 9-12 tops. Elementals are slightly higher in level
ygData.messageBody:
Nope, I'm a level 10 Necro and I was soloing drakes at 9. Even yellow ones. I'm
guessing that they are level 9-12 tops. Elementals are slightly higher in level and
require magical attack.

I'm guessing that the rock basilisks or rock snakes (I forgot their name) might be a
better kill for a level 14.

-Haytred
